{"tid":256586,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國大陸人口可能被高估, 印度將成人口最大國","createTime":"2017-05-24T15:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T16:15:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b01ba3fc5221338d30f216cd026c3ddb701ac17","tid":256586,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img5.cna.com.tw/www/webphotos/500/20170524/52309780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2Fwebphotos%2F500%2F20170524%2F52309780.jpg&h=d2468c7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（中央社台北24日電）一名中國人口學家表示，由於中國大陸官方對1990年到2016年的出生人口高估近9000萬人，中國大陸去年底實際人口應為12.9億人。若真如此，擁有13.3億人的印度將成為全世界人口最多的國家。<br />\n<br />\n英國金融時報發自北京報導指出，美國威斯康辛大學麥迪遜分校（University of Wisconsin-Madison）任職的中國大陸人口學家易富賢日前在北京向學界展示一項研究成果，凸顯中國大陸政策制定者面臨的人口危機。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，易富賢估計，中國大陸官員因為對生育率過於樂觀，導致在1990年到2016年間高估出生人口達9000萬人之多。他以2015年為例估算，中國大陸官方出生率估計為1.6，但易富賢認為實際上可能只有1.05。<br />\n<br />\n按照易富賢的估計，去年底中國大陸的人口並非官方的13.8億人，只有12.9億人。若以印度官方統計人口13.3億人來看，印度已經超越中國大陸，成為全球人口最多的國家。<br />\n<br />\n不過報導並未說明易富賢的理論基礎。報導也指出，多年來中國大陸官方很不歡迎易富賢的論調，他的書也一直到2013年才被解禁。不過隨著北京意識到一胎化政策的真正代價後，對易富賢的態度有所轉變。<br />\n<br />\n易富賢認為，如果沒有實施一胎化政策，中國大陸人口原本會在2040年達到16億人高峰後開始下降，從而讓這個全球第二大經濟體享受更長時間的人口紅利。1060524<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.cna.com.tw/news/acn/201705240257.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F201705240257.aspx&d=HruW1db70zuOHVo3azk41pnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=33a688bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.cna.com.tw/news/acn/201705240257.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"cab93076df82ece4c0cecc77e760869005b5a89b","tid":256586,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大陸唔係有身分證架咩<br />\n人口數都可以作數？"},{"pid":"8fd5a052cdf6e0801f1914d1708de9cef621cf48","tid":256586,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"口交部︰印度是中國不可分割的一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c5b0445259aa8abba68b3462c81e2a7ecad8b2","tid":256586,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a7b9cf766fed69e4700ac440a40b5ee7057373","tid":256586,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:51:51.000Z","msg":"同一時間, 好多超生既大陸人係無身份證<br />\n<br />\n法律上係不存在既人"},{"pid":"8ecff5e55bc3dd517c76cce5662aae3016b65f2e","tid":256586,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:57:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96e0e4960b2e6a230eb61a6406ce48aa2d9293d5","tid":256586,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T16:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>印度+中國已經有差唔多26億人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲要大部份都係垃圾人口<br />\n<br />\n真正有用既, 都唔知有冇260萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a2eda60873bd92ee9feb2fa07fc3c851a50bac","tid":256586,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T16:07:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同一時間, 好多超生既大陸人係無身份證<br />\n<br />\n法律上係不存在既人</blockquote><br />\n正想講"},{"pid":"c75a5f59f4a1f3b335e0f406fea9e9b927779560","tid":256586,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T16:09:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同一時間, 好多超生既大陸人係無身份證<br />\n<br />\n法律上係不存在既人</blockquote><br />\n正想講</blockquote><br />\n人哋人口學家會冇考慮呢點咩，人口係佢專業啊，至少都研究左十幾廿年以上啦"},{"pid":"55d21e0a01d8b77989aaa5dff4600f136f35abd8","tid":256586,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"